packOptions.summary: Cluster-compatible redis client including support for all redis data types, tagging mechanism, cache invalidation, PubSub, GeoSpatial indexes, HyperLogLog, BitFields and more.

title: CachingFramework.Redis
description: Redis client library based on StackExchange.Redis with features like an extensible serialization strategy, a tagging mechanism to group keys and hash fields, and more, all being cluster-compatible.
